            <title>[CODEC-218] Refactor HmacUtils methods into the HmacAlgorithms enum</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CODEC-218</link>
                <project id="12310464" key="CODEC">Commons Codec</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Refactor HmacUtils methods into the HmacAlgorithms enum.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adds to the enum:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;getHmac(byte[])&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;getName()&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hmac(byte[], byte[])&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hmac(byte[], InputStream)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hmac(String, String)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hmacHex(byte[], byte[])&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hmacHex(byte[], InputStream)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hmacHex(String, String)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
